{"tid":1976120,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"［重要］被控Telegram煽動縱火傷人 女侍應現面臨3項串謀煽惑罪 轉區院訊","createTime":"2020-04-17T04:33:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-17T05:00:23.000Z","uid":48083,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"417971d55de8c21ea0b4fc0fc6ea443201a87008","tid":1976120,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T04:33:21.000Z","msg":"有類同情況既手足睇路<br />\n<br />\nTelegram,連登一定有狗煽動<br />\n唔好見有人唔帶頭盔亂講野就跟機事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（獨媒特約報導）去年政府硬推《逃犯條例》修訂激發社會之間矛盾衝突，一名24歲女侍應被指在應用程式Telegram頻道發布煽動縱火和傷人的言論，今年初被起訴，還柙10多日後始獲高院批准保釋。案件今日在東區裁判法院再提堂，控方修訂控罪及新增兩項交替控罪，押後至5月5日轉區域法院訊，被告獲准以原有條件保釋。辯方表示保留提交不在場證明。<br />\n<br />\n報稱為侍應的許佩怡（24歲）原被控一項「煽惑他人縱火」及一項「煽惑他人傷人」罪。控方今修訂以上兩項控罪為「串謀煽惑他人犯縱火」罪及「串謀煽惑他人有意圖而傷人」，及新增一項「串謀煽惑他人犯刑事損壞」罪。另加兩項交替控罪，即「串謀作出具煽動意圖的作為」和「煽惑他人犯刑事損壞」罪。<br />\n<br />\n控罪指，許於去年8月12日至11月28日期間，在香港與其他人串謀非法煽惑Telegram的使用者，用火損壞屬於他人的財產、意圖導致他人身體受嚴重傷害而非法及惡意傷人，以及損壞他人的財產。<br />\n<br />\n兩項交替控罪指，許於去年8月12日至11月28日期間在香港，與其他人串謀作出具煽動意圖的作為，即非法煽惑Telegram的使用者使用暴力；以及於去年9月3日在香港，非法煽惑Telegram的使用者損壞屬於他人的財產，即一部載有Whatsapp的裝置。據了解，被告被指控在Telegram發布一個電話號碼並鼓勵網民向該電話發訊息。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：ESCC87/2020<br />\n<br />\n記者：黎彩燕<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1072528\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1072528&d=5Vq0xNKZ3qFPdYugipJU9wp4YzggAwntK9UjHSQ2u7w%3D&h=922b9dcc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1072528&h=9635d232\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1072528</a>"},{"pid":"7e8f64f1c35815d37d4f429b7515d004fc78cc22","tid":1976120,"uid":35430,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T04:37:01.000Z","msg":"死黑警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb44809fe2a8386aef16dc7ab4e959e7b0a2f803","tid":1976120,"uid":92385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T04:45:23.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"bae53ddcea2d362b06307f6944d709b6a981dbc2","tid":1976120,"uid":45914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T04:45:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"09761aee866a12bae08032c76aafaff9b366c9f0","tid":1976120,"uid":76078,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T04:50:04.000Z","msg":"鼓勵網民向該電話發訊息 = 非法煽惑 損壞屬於他人的一部載有Whatsapp的裝置 ?<br />\n<br />\n咁樣上D court <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f008b4e31ef6de8192db941782cf63435a4304d","tid":1976120,"uid":113155,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T04:53:10.000Z","msg":"其實咁同23條有分別？<br />\n網上講嘢不嬲係不負責任，啲網上欺凌捉咗未，全世界要坐監啦。<br />\n以tg whatsapp 對話當裁決證據？<br />\n屌，真係痴撚線。"},{"pid":"14d500b176a97e98486ee0f12655532de7a965a6","tid":1976120,"uid":283207,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T04:54:06.000Z","msg":"以為9up冇人知咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過唔割，手足黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f5691e735c8cd7a28d61856f4a3251e82dbff04","tid":1976120,"uid":14422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T04:55:15.000Z","msg":"唔係香港就冇問題？<br />\n<br />\n控罪指，許於去年8月12日至11月28日期間，在香港與其他人"},{"pid":"bac28fc6734483d0df429462dcb2c9f60344b844","tid":1976120,"uid":171058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T04:57:15